OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780661502
OL,3,CBritish Heart Foundation to close 150
OL,4,Ccharity shops
OL,6,FThe British Heart Foundation (BHF) is
OL,7,Fset to close 150 charity shops in the
OL,8,Fnext two years as it continues to face
OL,9,Fan "exceptionally challenging trading
OL,10,Fenvironment".
OL,12,FThe charity is proposing the closures
OL,13,Fto make sure its shop network "remains
OL,14,Fcommercially sustainable" to support
OL,15,Fits fundraising efforts, it said.
OL,17,FIt involves shutting down 90 stores by
OL,18,Fthe end of March next year, and the
OL,19,Frest by March 2028.
OL,26,@uD@_OUvD@YO]
