FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780661502
OL,3,CBritish Heart Foundation to close 150
OL,4,Ccharity shops
OL,6,FThe organisation said the plan follows
OL,7,Fa review of rising operating costs and
OL,8,Fchanging customer habits, which have
OL,9,Fmeant some stores are "no longer
OL,10,Ffinancially sustainable".
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThere will also be cuts to the
OL,18,Fcharity's central teams and functions
OL,19,Fwhich support the retail division, but
OL,20,Fit has not disclosed how many workers
OL,21,Fwill be impacted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
