OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780661502
OL,3,CBritish Heart Foundation to close 150
OL,4,Ccharity shops
OL,6,FThe BHF currently has 640 shops across
OL,7,Fthe UK, which are run with support
OL,8,Ffrom volunteers and raise funds to
OL,9,Fsupport the charity's research into
OL,10,Fcardiovascular disease.
OL,12,F"Our shops mean so much to our
OL,13,Fcolleagues, brilliant volunteers and
OL,14,Fcommunities across the UK," chief
OL,15,Fexecutive Dr Charmaine Griffiths said.
OL,17,F"They are places where people come
OL,18,Ftogether to donate, shop and
OL,19,Fvolunteer, helping to make a real
OL,20,Fdifference to lives affected by
OL,21,Fcardiovascular disease.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780661502
OL,3,CBritish Heart Foundation to close 150
OL,4,Ccharity shops
OL,6,F"We know this will be a difficult time
OL,7,Ffor our dedicated colleagues and
OL,8,Fvolunteers in affected stores and
OL,9,Femphasise our deep appreciation and
OL,10,Fgratitude for all they have done for
OL,11,FBHF and the communities they serve.
OL,13,F"Cardiovascular disease remains one of
OL,14,Fthe UK's biggest killers and our
OL,15,Fpriority is funding research to save
OL,16,Flives.
OL,18,F"We must take the difficult step to
OL,19,Fclose some of our shops to sustain
OL,20,Fretail's important contribution to
OL,21,Ffunding BHF's groundbreaking research."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
