FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780661502
OL,3,CBritish Heart Foundation to close 150
OL,4,Ccharity shops
OL,6,FThe news comes as Cancer Research UK
OL,7,Fshut down 90 shops by May this year,
OL,8,Fwith plans to close 100 more by April
OL,9,F2027, citing mounting financial
OL,10,Fpressures on high streets across the
OL,11,FUK.
OL,13,FThe charity said those closed down
OL,14,Fwere selected based on their financial
OL,15,Fperformance, lease agreements and
OL,16,Fgeographical position.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
